title: Claude is still <2026-06-01 Mon> much slower than ChatGPT.
pid: 5731c06c-7ac3-4e03-85ea-8bbcf98f4c9d
body: |2-
  I switch to ChatGPT for a month after hitting Claude usage limits.
  During that time Anthropic got more compute from SpaceX.
  I switched back today and already regret it, because it's slow.
